{"id": 697, "genre": 1001, "title": "在你找旅行攻略的时候，你无法忍受什么？", "description": "生活研究所不定期会推出当季应景并充满正义感的“无！法！忍！受！”小调查，欢迎来表态。", "record_count": 4610, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194403lYxL0XK8PRp2Hu1U.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-13T01:04:06Z", "options": [{"id": 34049, "content": "自助游的游记点进去却是跟团……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279916}, {"id": 34310, "content": "是外语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257106}, {"id": 34060, "content": "游记&攻略貌似该做区分，以应对不同需求！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133297}, {"id": 33805, "content": "机场也要留个影", "image": null, "praise_count": 317, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171364}, {"id": 33806, "content": "不关注‘去乐园亲子互动平台’", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336413}, {"id": 33809, "content": "我想知道自驾游的内容结果全特喵的抱团游", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340997}, {"id": 34065, "content": "心情、景点、线路、美食、照片各种介绍分段不清，题图不配。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355971}, {"id": 33812, "content": "配的照片太丑。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 34068, "content": "除了美化后的图片，就剩概括性的赞美，我要去玩还能不知道风景秀丽景色独好？用你BB，有用信息一概没有，住宿环境，消费水平都没有，我只希望知道酒店位置，价格，门票，美食街，商圈和交通啊？", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211928QBuha0mJ8WpCl6eN.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357973}, {"id": 33813, "content": "一堆旅行中的琐事但却毫无重点（也可能那真的只是游记。。。）", "image": null, "praise_count": 277, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98651}, {"id": 34069, "content": "飞机几乎全是夜班飞机……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357976}, {"id": 33814, "content": "没钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 259, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354971}, {"id": 37399, "content": "穷游 还旅个毛游啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391846}, {"id": 33818, "content": "仔细看一遍没看懂 一点帮助没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141365}, {"id": 33819, "content": "整篇文章提到的全是美食和名胜古迹，能不能有点其他方面的推荐", "image": null, "praise_count": 188, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342019}, {"id": 119323, "content": "照片太丑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438614}, {"id": 33820, "content": "钱不够。", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147567}, {"id": 33821, "content": "我一个人去却看到全篇秀恩爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 209, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355023}, {"id": 34077, "content": "自拍太丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358020}, {"id": 34078, "content": "全部都是自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358022}, {"id": 33823, "content": "全是废话 推荐个饭店 连地址都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 401, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275208}, {"id": 33825, "content": "都是大腿", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119650}, {"id": 33827, "content": "通篇都在卖萌说一堆废话，要不就是和以前的旅行经历对比。a的街道整洁比b好多了，h地的m旅馆的服务比j地的差远了，比拉巴拉的……谁是来听这个的啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 185, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139738}, {"id": 33828, "content": "钱不够，漂亮的地方太要钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348735}, {"id": 34341, "content": "全尼玛是自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349560}, {"id": 33830, "content": "更喜欢宅在家里", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144289}, {"id": 33831, "content": "全是照骗，没有任何指导性内容…", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212665}, {"id": 33833, "content": "流水账似的。没有行程规划。", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355088}, {"id": 34089, "content": "流水账", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358103}, {"id": 33835, "content": "整容怪的美图秀秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347780}, {"id": 33836, "content": "旁边人甩手掌柜，但还要指手画脚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301696}, {"id": 33838, "content": "换个大点的平台秀自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330266}, {"id": 34350, "content": "只有美女，没有攻略；po酒店，不告诉酒店名称的都是耍流氓！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360385}, {"id": 35375, "content": "在机场秀个飞机图…其实特么就是去送人的，然后各种网上当图片发！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281714}, {"id": 33842, "content": "最讨厌那种一直在晒买的东西和吃的的攻略，最后一大堆的感想，怎么去的，哪里好玩一概没讲，难道让我自己去猜吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346585}, {"id": 35123, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 368130}, {"id": 34357, "content": "没有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360464}, {"id": 33846, "content": "对老年人旅游方略大都嗤之以鼻、弃之不顾、这块蛋糕也不小喔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334052}, {"id": 33848, "content": "没有吃的介绍！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340669}, {"id": 33850, "content": "秀自拍 秀n个人的大合照！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355212}, {"id": 33852, "content": "都是很贵的饭店和酒店，我们又不是富二代", "image": null, "praise_count": 162, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355218}, {"id": 36413, "content": "有想旅游的心 没有旅游的钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341288}, {"id": 34366, "content": "种类太多，各种不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360552}, {"id": 34878, "content": "攻略全部做好了，精细到每两个目的地之间打车大概多少钱，他们罗列的那些有名的必去地如果要去可能会遇到什么问题，根据他们可能会希望的游玩时间制定了PlanA-C,以及对各种天气做出的相应的调整方案，等等等等。天知道我搞到那些数据废了多大劲儿。在这一切的一切准备就绪后，我满心欢喜地在群里告诉他们，我开始订酒店和机票了，紧接着所有人开始用各式各样的理由，说着各式各样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365915}, {"id": 33862, "content": "写的没有逻辑", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355305}, {"id": 33866, "content": "说半天没说什么，景点行程什么都没说，介绍的东西也没个消费范围…还全是文艺小自拍……学生党没钱不懂啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 320009}, {"id": 33869, "content": "不看攻略的表示最讨厌一直说心情…", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354162}, {"id": 119120, "content": "心灵鸡汤太多，我不想知道你是不是成为了更好的自己，我只想知道干货。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760529}, {"id": 33874, "content": "介绍这个多好吃 那个住的非常方便 却没有地址～", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354174}, {"id": 33878, "content": "千万完语都在表达自己的心情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 353789}]}